title: Winning numbers drawn in 'SuperCash' game
maintext:
MADISON, Wis. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Wisconsin Lottery’s “SuperCash” game were:
03-06-13-25-31-33, Doubler: N
(three, six, thirteen, twenty-five, thirty-one, thirty-three; Doubler: N)
¶ Maximum prize: $350,000
